Class ExportContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cafean.client.validation.ExportContext
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ModelElement, java.lang.Comparable<ExportContext>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GenericTableContext, PropertyContext
    public abstract class ExportContext
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<ExportContext>, ModelElement
    The base class for simple objects that correlate positions in the ASCII view of a model to the properties and graphical editors in the user interface.
    See Also:
    ContextWriter, ValidationDisplayPanel
